{
  "stem": "26142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was straw in-- in the place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We fell down with our-- with our poor [NON-ENGLISH] that we had with us and from-- from great exhaustion and-- and-- and I remember, I fell-- we fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What happened to the rest of the people, we never saw them again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We never know what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It-- it must have been midday, next day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It must have been midday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we heard a-- a-- a lot of clattering, awesome wagon clattering coming closer, closer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Coming and stopped at that barn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He opened the door.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And a guy comes in and he saw us there and he says [SPEAKING NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "What are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We started to-- to plead with him and explain to him that we were attacked here and-- and we had nowhere else to go and-- and-- and so that we came in here.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we said we would-- we would pay him if he would take us to the next little place that is called [?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Istichka. ?] Because we found that out from the previous place, from the mayor's sons that there is a small village called [?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Istichka. ?] There are Jews in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we figured we wanted to get to, more or less, to a Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so he saw-- he saw that we had-- we had a woolen blanket rolled up that we had-- we had with us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said he would take us there if we give him that blanket and a pair of under-- underpants.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we agreed to that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We'll give him the blanket.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We'll give him the underpants.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said, it's only about five, six kilometers from here, this [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Istichka. ?] But he said he wouldn't do that now.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
